 1. Perused the reports of the Official
 Liquidator dated 23rd May 2003 and 29th April 2005
 as well as two letters sent by Shri Ashwin M.Desai
 dated 1st April 2005 and 13th April 2005
 respectively.
 : 2 :
 2. The allegation made in these two letters
 have already been considered by this Court and the
 decision of this Court dated 26th November 2001 in
 Company Application No.179 of 1986 has become
 final. If the Complainant had any grievance about
 the correctness of the said decision, he could have
 taken recourse to appropriate remedy as was
 available to him in law. Any further letter
 received from Shri Ashwin M.Desai on this subject,
 shall be consigned to the record.
 3. Both the Reports disposed of accordingly.
 A.M.KHANWILKAR, J.
